headline.print_headline: Rooney Back for Manchester Derby but Falcao Unfit
headline.main: Rooney Back for Manchester Derby but Falcao Unfit

lead_paragraph: Wayne Rooney, who has scored more goals than anyone in the Manchester derby, is back after suspension and fit for Sunday's meeting between the city's two biggest clubs at the Etihad Stadium.
